Two resulting solutions, heated up to 58 C before the reaction, were mixed under the stirring with 0 rpm, while the temperature kept unchanged. To synthesize the CaCO3 nanoparticles we use the co-precipitation technique. 20 mkl of  0.375 % wt. Two resulting solutions were mixed under the stirring with 0 rpm during 8 min 20 sec min, solutions were heated to 68 C previous.
